	   <tr><td colspan=2>I dual wield this weapon with a sash of the dragonborn and it procs quite often. Good thing that rangers get Jolt at level 51. I sometimes outdamage the main tank and have to re-jolt to keep agro off, but as jolt is a low mana spell, i don't have a prob with re-jolting and dont usually take alot of hits in group situations where i am assisting a main tank like a good lil ranger. Hey, if i want to solo, I go to DL and summon tons of arrows with a tolan bracer and fill a mob with arrows. &lt;BTW takes about 12 stacks of summoned arrows to kill a ravishing drolvarg in DL with a 52 ranger with 201 archery and a blessed faydark thunderbolt&gt; <br>Melekin Trailstalker-52 Pathfinder &lt;E Marr server&gt;<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
